<bibRefCitation author="Katoh, T. K. &amp; Zhang, G. &amp; Zhou, C. J. &amp; Gao, J. J." box="[659,864,1053,1079]" pageId="7" pageNumber="120" pagination="345 - 365" refId="ref12809" refString="Katoh, T. K., Zhang, G., Zhou, C. J. &amp; Gao, J. J. (2018) Taxonomy of the Hirtodrosophila melanderi species group (Diptera: Drosophilidae), with descriptions of four new species from southwestern China. Zootaxa, 4422 (3), 345 - 365. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4422.3.2" type="journal article" year="2018">
